# ============================================================================
# Azure Logic App Integration with AI Foundry - Environment Configuration
# Azure Logic App 與 AI Foundry 整合 - 環境變數設定檔
# ============================================================================
# 
# 說明 (Description):
# 此檔案包含執行 Azure Logic App 整合範例所需的所有環境變數。
# This file contains all environment variables required to run the Azure Logic App integration samples.
#
# 使用方式 (Usage):
# 1. 複製此檔案並重新命名為 .env
#    Copy this file and rename it to .env
# 2. 填入您的實際值（移除 "your-" 前綴）
#    Fill in your actual values (remove "your-" prefix)
# 3. 確保 .env 檔案已加入 .gitignore，避免洩漏敏感資訊
#    Ensure .env file is added to .gitignore to prevent exposing sensitive information
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# Section 1: Azure AI Foundry Project Configuration
# 區段 1: Azure AI Foundry 專案設定
# ============================================================================

# PROJECT_ENDPOINT (必要 / Required)
# Azure AI Foundry 專案端點 URL
# Your Azure AI Foundry project endpoint URL
# 
# 取得方式 (How to obtain):
# 1. 前往 Azure AI Foundry Studio (https://ai.azure.com)
#    Go to Azure AI Foundry Studio (https://ai.azure.com)
# 2. 選擇您的專案 (Select your project)
# 3. 在專案設定中找到端點 URL (Find endpoint URL in project settings)
# 
# 格式範例 (Format example):
# https://your-project-name.cognitiveservices.azure.com/
#
# 使用於 (Used in):
# - cli_logic_apps.py
# - ui_logic_apps.py
PROJECT_ENDPOINT=your-project-endpoint-here

# MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME (必要 / Required)
# Azure AI 模型部署名稱
# Your Azure AI model deployment name
#
# 取得方式 (How to obtain):
# 1. 前往 Azure AI Foundry Studio
#    Go to Azure AI Foundry Studio
# 2. 選擇您的專案 > Deployments (選擇您的專案 > 部署)
#    Select your project > Deployments
# 3. 複製模型部署名稱 (Copy the model deployment name)
#
# 支援的模型 (Supported models):
# - gpt-4o
# - gpt-4o-mini
# - gpt-4 turbo
# - gpt-35-turbo
#
# 使用於 (Used in):
# - cli_logic_apps.py
# - ui_logic_apps.py
MODEL_DEPLOYMENT_NAME=your-model-deployment-name

# ============================================================================
# Section 2: Azure Subscription and Resource Group Configuration
# 區段 2: Azure 訂閱與資源群組設定
# ============================================================================
AZURE_SUBSCRIPTION_ID=your-azure-subscription-id
AZURE_RESOURCE_GROUP=your-resource-group-name

# ============================================================================
# Section 3: Azure Logic App Configuration
# 區段 3: Azure Logic App 設定
# ============================================================================

# LOGIC_APP_NAME (必要 / Required)
# Logic App 名稱
# Your Logic App name
#
# 取得方式 (How to obtain):
# 1. 前往 Azure Portal
#    Go to Azure Portal
# 2. 導航至 Logic Apps
#    Navigate to Logic Apps
# 3. 複製您要使用的 Logic App 名稱
#    Copy the name of the Logic App you want to use
#
# 或使用 Azure CLI (Or use Azure CLI):
# az logic workflow list --resource-group <your-resource-group> --query "[].name" -o table
#
# 前置需求 (Prerequisites):
# - Logic App 必須已經建立並設定好 HTTP 觸發器和 Office 365 Outlook 動作
#   Logic App must be created with HTTP trigger and Office 365 Outlook action configured
# - 參考 README.md 中的「使用指南 > 前置準備」
#   Refer to "Usage Guide > Prerequisites" in README.md
#
# 使用於 (Used in):
# - cli_logic_apps.py
# - ui_logic_apps.py
# - user_logic_apps.py (AzureLogicAppTool.register_logic_app)
LOGIC_APP_NAME=your-logic-app-name

# TRIGGER_NAME (必要 / Required)
# Logic App HTTP 觸發器名稱
# Your Logic App HTTP trigger name
#
# 取得方式 (How to obtain):
# 1. 前往 Azure Portal > Logic Apps
#    Go to Azure Portal > Logic Apps
# 2. 開啟您的 Logic App
#    Open your Logic App
# 3. 在 Logic App Designer 中展開 HTTP 觸發器
#    Expand HTTP trigger in Logic App Designer
# 4. 觸發器名稱顯示在標題列
#    Trigger name is shown in the title bar
#
# 預設值 (Default value):
# When_a_HTTP_request_is_received
#
# 注意 (Note):
# - 觸發器名稱區分大小寫 (Trigger name is case-sensitive)
# - 空格會被轉換為底線 (Spaces are converted to underscores)
#
# 使用於 (Used in):
# - cli_logic_apps.py
# - ui_logic_apps.py
# - user_logic_apps.py (AzureLogicAppTool.register_logic_app)
TRIGGER_NAME=When_a_HTTP_request_is_received

# RECIPIENT_EMAIL (必要 / Required)
# 預設收件人電子郵件地址
# Default recipient email address
#
# 說明 (Description):
# 此電子郵件地址將用作 Logic App 發送電子郵件的預設收件人
# This email address will be used as the default recipient for Logic App emails
#
# 格式範例 (Format example):
# user@example.com
# john.doe@company.com
#
# 注意 (Note):
# - 確保收件人地址有效 (Ensure the recipient address is valid)
# - 檢查垃圾郵件資料夾以確認收到測試郵件
#   Check spam folder to confirm test emails are received
# - 可以在函數調用時覆寫此預設值
#   This default can be overridden when calling functions
#
# 使用於 (Used in):
# - cli_logic_apps.py
# - ui_logic_apps.py
# - 所有預設任務按鈕 (All default task buttons)
RECIPIENT_EMAIL=your-recipient@example.com

# ============================================================================
# Section 4: Azure Authentication (Optional)
# 區段 4: Azure 認證設定（選用）
# ============================================================================

# 本範例使用 DefaultAzureCredential 進行認證
# This sample uses DefaultAzureCredential for authentication
#
# 支援的認證方式 (Supported authentication methods):
# 1. Azure CLI: az login
# 2. Managed Identity (在 Azure 服務上執行時 / When running on Azure services)
# 3. Environment variables (如下設定 / Configure as below)
# 4. Visual Studio Code
# 5. Azure PowerShell
#
# 如需使用環境變數認證，請取消註解並填入以下欄位:
# To use environment variable authentication, uncomment and fill in the following:
#
# AZURE_TENANT_ID=your-tenant-id
# AZURE_CLIENT_ID=your-client-id
# AZURE_CLIENT_SECRET=your-client-secret
#
# 取得方式 (How to obtain):
# 1. 前往 Azure Portal > Azure Active Directory > App registrations
#    Go to Azure Portal > Azure Active Directory > App registrations
# 2. 建立或選擇應用程式註冊 (Create or select an app registration)
# 3. 複製 Tenant ID 和 Application (client) ID
#    Copy Tenant ID and Application (client) ID
# 4. 在 Certificates & secrets 中建立 Client secret
#    Create a Client secret in Certificates & secrets
#
# 所需權限 (Required permissions):
# - Logic Apps: Microsoft.Logic/workflows/read
# - Logic Apps: Microsoft.Logic/workflows/triggers/listCallbackUrl/action
# - AI Foundry: Cognitive Services User or Contributor

